tendo-a-boost-as-switch-sales-continue-to-dwindle-112508240.html"><em>《塞尔达传说：王国之泪》</em></a>等 2023 年推出的游戏的兴趣。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> Switch 销量预测的提高正值游戏玩家热切等待<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nintendo-is-said-to-be-showing-the-switch-2s-dlss-and-ray-tracing-capabilities-to-developers-161050817.html">Switch 的继任者</a>之际。虽然任天堂尚未发布任何实质性信息，但据报道该游戏系统将于今年某个时候推出（届时将面临比其前身更加拥挤的市场）。据称，开发者在 2023 年 8 月的 Gamescom 闭门会议上看到了 Switch 2（由于缺乏具体名称）。据说他们看到了<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/how-this-non-gamer-fell-in-love-with-the-legend-of-zelda-breath-of-the-wild-123054845.html"><em>《塞尔达传说：荒野之息》</em></a>的一个版本<em>&nbsp;</em>具有比原版 Switch 更高的帧速率和分辨率。据报道，该演示还展示了即将推出的 Switch 的虚幻引擎 5、光线追踪、NVIDIA 的 DLSS 升级技术以及与 PS5 和 Series X 类似的视觉质量。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/nintendo- believes-itll-sell-more-switch-consoles-than-first-thought-095017928.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/nintendo-believes-itll-sell-more-switch-consoles-than-first-thought-095017928.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 87b91e09-2055-45d8-9ec9-3b08ebe93733 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Sarah Fielding]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 06 Feb 2024 09:50:17 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1707215348</ingested><modified> 2024-02-06T10:29:15+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Investment & Company Information]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-06%2Fbe2a8a20-152b-11ee-bf27-53892d751f49&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=f687bb5462eac7ec4862f1451a92a232c9d5980e" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-06%2Fbe2a8a20-152b-11ee-bf27-53892d751f49&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=da76e9f068fa10efb2608597e28d48602f214195" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Kris Naudus / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Nintendo Switch and Switch OLED sitting atop a collection of games.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Nintendo Switch and Switch OLED]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Apple Vision Pro users will have to go to a store to reset forgotten passcodes]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>您能想象因为您忘记了指定的使用密码而不得不邮寄一个价值 3,499 美元的小工具吗？如果购买了<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-vision-pro-hands-on-redux-immersive-video-disney-app-floating-keyboard-and-a-little-screaming-180006222.html?_fsig=6H2AJpNq5n77Zm1Wbvxy8A--%7EA">Apple Vision Pro 的</a>客户忘记了设备的密码，他们可能必须这样做。据<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/forgot-your-apple-vision-pro-s-passcode-you-may-have-to-take-it-back-to-store?sref=10lNAhZ9"><em>彭博社</em></a>报道，该公司一直告诉买家，重置代码的唯一方法是前往 Apple Store 零售店或将混合现实耳机邮寄给 AppleCare 客户支持。然后，苹果将重置他们的代码，以便他们可以再次使用他们的设备。</p><p>正如<em>彭博社</em>指出的那样，如果用户多次输入错误代码，他们的设备将被禁用，并且他们必须等待一段时间才能重试。如果他们在等待期后仍然无法回忆起代码，则必须让苹果重置他们的代码，而让苹果这样做将删除他们耳机上的所有内容。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>值得注意的是， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2Rpc2N1c3Npb25zLmFwcGxlLmNvbS90aHJlYWQvMjU1NDU1MDg4P3NvcnRCeT1iZXN0IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3ODVkZDY3Yi01OGVjLTRhYmEtYTcwMC1iOWM4MzBkYjA0NWIifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAabaeiDDcEOCHaSQzrmp1XlfFgznPY6g8ZnkK2XiOL-M&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscussions.apple.com%2Fthread%2F255455088%3FsortBy%3Dbest" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://discussions.apple.com/thread/255455088?sortBy=best">苹果论坛</a>上的一些用户即使输入了正确的密码，仍然被锁定——目前还不清楚这是否是一个影响某些设备的错误——所以这个问题可能发生在任何人身上。根据其他一些帖子，苹果的 Genius Bar 人员使用一种名为“开发者带”的配件，该公司以 299 美元的价格向开发者出售该配件，将耳机连接到 iPad 或笔记本电脑，以便能够重置它。据报道，至少在一个例子中，苹果天才<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:;cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2Rpc2N1c3Npb25zLmFwcGxlLmNvbS90aHJlYWQvMjU1NDU1MDg4P2Fuc3dlcklkPTI2MDE0MTU5NzAyMiZzb3J0Qnk9YmVzdCMyNjAxNDE1OTcwMjIiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6Ijc4NWRkNjdiLTU4ZWMtNGFiYS1hNzAwLWI5YzgzMGRiMDQ1YiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAe1wWq3_nj7UXXDvqTEmd3bfXe7MXDXD-LuR0xtEf7Jq&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscussions.apple.com%2Fthread%2F255455088%3FanswerId%3D260141597022%26sortBy%3Dbest%23260141597022" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://discussions.apple.com/thread/255455088?answerId=260141597022&amp;sortBy=best#260141597022">未能重置</a>用户的耳机，而不得不完全更换它。</p><p>更改耳机密码的过程在未来仍可能发生变化——毕竟，最近发布的 Vision Pro 是全新产品类别的第一次迭代。为了那些已经购买了它的人，我们希望它是通过软件更新引入的，而不是作为下一版本的改进。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/apple-vision-pro-users-will-have-to-go-to-a-store-to-reset-forgotten-passcodes-070101287.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apple-vision-pro-users-will-have-to-go-to-a-store-to-reset-forgotten-passcodes-070101287.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 785dd67b-58ec-4aba-a700-b9c830db045b</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mariella Moon]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 06 Feb 2024 07:01:01 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1707200565</ingested><modified> 2024-02-06T06:22:50+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2Fbce94110-c4b2-11ee-befb-a8c6fc5e422f&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=db7a5bd6e4e49e987764535231a615c968808c19" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2Fbce94110-c4b2-11ee-befb-a8c6fc5e422f&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=c7fd18bc4d6974ebedbac4e9e8f2d8e7c82af48e" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[NDZ/STAR MAX/IPx]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Photo by: NDZ/STAR MAX/IPx 2024 2/3/24 The Apple Vision Pro headset is seen on display at the Fifth Avenue Apple store in New York City. The Vision Pro, the tech giant's $3,499 headset, is its first major release since the Apple Watch nine years ago.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Vision Pro at the Apple Fifth Avenue store on Februay 3, 2024]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Roblox adds real-time AI chat translation using its own language model]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/roblox/"><em>Roblox</em></a>目前为超过 7000 万每日活跃用户提供服务，自 2006 年 9 月推出以来（近 18 年前）仍然表现强劲。开发团队现在正进一步发展该平台的庞大社区，通过提供实时人工智能聊天翻译来连接世界各地的游戏玩家。 CTO Daniel Sturman <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://blog.roblox.com/2024/02/breaking-down-language-barriers-with-a-multilingual-translation-model/">表示</a>，他的团队需要构建自己的“统一的、基于 Transformer 的翻译 LLM（大型语言模型）”，以便无缝处理<em>Roblox</em>支持的所有 16 种语言，并识别<em>Roblox</em>特定的俚语和缩写（笔者刚刚了解到“obby”指的是游戏中的障碍场）。</p><p>因此，聊天窗口始终以用户自己的语言显示对话 - 延迟很小，约为 100 毫秒，因此几乎是实时的。您还可以单击每行左侧的翻译图标以查看其原始语言。 Sturman 声称，由于该语言模型的高效架构和迭代训练，它“在<em>Roblox</em>内容上的表现优于商业翻译 API”。开发团队稍后将推出反馈工具，以帮助提高翻译质量，此外还会不断更新平台上出现的任何新流行语。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-01/5611ba20-c4ae-11ee-aff6-d459412050ea" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-01/5611ba20-c4ae-11ee-aff6-d459412050ea" style="height:548px;width:1002px;" alt="Roblox 构建了自己的大型语言模型，支持其平台上所有 16 种语言的实时聊天翻译。它可以识别 Roblox 特定的俚语和缩写。" data-uuid="601bcb7b-0612-3767-8a58-ba12f94a55a6"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">罗布乐思</div></figure><p><em>Roblox 的</em>翻译工作并不止于此。 Sturman 补充说，他的团队已经在研究自动翻译“图像、纹理、3D 模型上的文本”等。由于<em>Roblox</em>支持语音聊天，该高管还透露了自动语音聊天翻译的可能性，因此来自世界各地的游戏玩家可以在平台上用自己的语言无缝地相互交谈。鉴于三星已经通过<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-s24-and-s24-review-a-taste-of-generative-ai-in-everyday-use-160041639.html">Galaxy AI</a>提供了类似的功能，可能用不了多久我们就会听到<em>Roblox</em>在这方面的另一次更新。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/roblox-adds-real-time-ai-chat-translation-using-its-own-language-model-061929902.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/roblox-adds-real-time-ai-chat-translation-using-its-own-language-model-061929902.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> bc045d30-f848-4299-ac5f-3d3df70feaa9 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Richard Lai]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 06 Feb 2024 06:19:29 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1707200372</ingested><modified> 2024-02-06T06:19:41+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Personal Investing Ideas & Strategies]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Richard Lai]]></category><media:content height="875" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-02%2F03e22fe0-c4af-11ee-adff-9468c1f43e8d&amp;resize=1400%2C875&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=3c12784eb39ac36234f4312714163dc6ef5d706e" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="875" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-02%2F03e22fe0-c4af-11ee-adff-9468c1f43e8d&amp;resize=1400%2C875&amp;cli